				<li>adding an activity with a submitted status (complete)</li></ul>
    	<li><strong>Receive Item</strong>: add due date, local itemID number for checkout (complete)</li>
    	<li><strong>Return Item</strong> (complete)</li>
    	<li><strong>View Requests</strong>: basic queries based on pre-defined parameters</li>
    	<li><strong>Cancel Request</strong> (complete)</li>
	</ul>

<h3>Phase 2</h3>

<ul>
	<li><strong>New Request</strong>
		<ul><li>pull bibliographic data from WorldCat via API (complete)</li>
		<li>bookmarklet to launch new request from WorldCat (complete)</li></ul>
